Celebrity nightclub owner, Pascal Okechukwu aka Cubana Chief Priest has described possessing a ‘summer body’ without ‘summer money’ as useless. The socialite, who’s in Turkey, shared a photo where he sat near the seaside as he treated himself to some delicacies Flaunting his ‘bold’ shirtless body, Dr Ezemuo dissed individuals who strive to achieve summer bodies without money to accompany same.   I never slept with your friend, ex-husband replies Kaffy     Simi, Adekunle celebrate daughter at two     Mr Sabinus sues Peak, Gala over alleged intellectual theft   He said: “You Have Summer Body But You Don’t Have Summer Money. No Be Juju Be That. How & Where You Wan Go Show The Body?” Chief priest advised people to put in same amount of energy into amassing riches like they do in achieving great summer bodies else it’ll be worthless. “Hustle Oh!!!! Make Your Summer Body No End For Bar Beach. As You Dey Hustle For Better Body No Forget To Get Plenty Money,” he added.